SUMMARY:Columbia Employee Store Passes for PHMG: Until March 22nd
DESCRIPTION:The Portland Hiking Meetup Group\nOnce again we have Columbia Employee Store passes for our group. Thanks to Brian Hoffman who worked with them to provide Portland Hiking group (PHMG) members passes to visit their store and avail of discounts they offer.\n\n\\*\\***Note**: This is not an actual hosted event. You can just download pass and visit the store any time between Feb 22nd through March 22nd 2026.\n\n**Columbia Employee Store Invitation Details:**\n\n* **Valid Dates:** February 27th - March 22nd\n* **Discount:** Enjoy 40% off storewide\n* **Our Annual Winter Tent Sale is on now through March 8—invite your friends and family to shop the tent and save up to 70% off\, no pass needed.**\n* **Brands:** Shop the latest styles from Columbia\, SOREL\, Mountain Hardwear\, and prAna\n* **How to Use:** Show the digital pass on your phone or bring a printed copy + proof of affiliation\n* **Guest Policy:** Bring up to four guests per visit\n* **Note:** For Employee Store access only (not valid online)\n\n**Download the attached pass on your phone (or take a printout) when you go to the store (see attached photo)**\n\n*Note that this is just an opportunity to check out Columbia Employee Store\, that they extend to a lot of other groups\, and some of our members may want to buy outdoor products at a discount.* ***Neither Brian or Avinash are promoting Columbia or have received any compensation.***
